<p>Just add water and a couple of drops of essential oil to create an instant mood-booster to any room </p>

<p>Another agreed, writing: 'This is a very small fragrance diffuser, with very low sound, and various colours of lights make the room very beautiful. After adding essential oils, it emits a very fragrant smell and can work for several hours.' </p>

<p>You can swap and change the essential oils according to your needs. Lavender oil is known for its calming and relaxing properties- great if you're looking to de-stress, while Tea Tree is invigorating and cleansing. You'll need to buy the oils separately. </p>

<p>Many shoppers have praised the CkeyiN Mini Essential Oil Diffuser for its ability to create a 'therapeutic and cosy' space. </p>

<p>One shopper described it as 'very calming, should have bought one sooner!' They went on to write 'Suffering from anxiety this relaxes and calms me during each and every evening, and now I just don't know why I waited so long to get one!'</p>

<p>Another agreed, writing: 'Great companion for working from home. I bought this for my home office during coronavirus period. I find it very calming with its changing light colours and discreet mist. I connected it to my laptop, and it lasts from morning till evening. I put a few drops of orange essential oil. Small and cute design too.'</p>

